FILENAME: /maps/gg_sp_arena_v1.bsp
FILESIZE: 701,628 bytes (685 KB)
DATE RELEASED: 23 August 2008

CREDITS: This map was the result of many peoples insperation.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Extract all contents of the .zip file directly into your "\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\YOURNAMEHERE\counter-strike source\cstrike\" folder.

DESCRIPTION: A GunGame maps made for those that like lots of heights. Features a great center knifing platform for those KNIFE PRO servers. Offers medium size playing field with easy navigation through out the whole map. Has lots of great spots for snipering or all out open war.

COMMENTS: No third-party/third-person testing was done before the release of this map. If you have any problems, tell me on my FPSBanana page ("WEBSITE"), or e-mail me. Copyright 2008 Turtle Productions rights reserved.

Please Post Any Feedback
